cu.explanation_en: Setting the integrity algorithm to the unknown enum 'nia9' will cause negotiation failure during the security negotiation phase and NAS registration rejection.

du.explanation_en: Setting dl_carrierBandwidth to 300 (exceeds maximum allowed bandwidth) will cause configuration validation failure in the downlink carrier configuration.
du.explanation_zh: 將 dl_carrierBandwidth 設定為 300（超過最大允許頻寬）會在下行載波配置中導致配置驗證失敗。
